# Project Zomboid B42 Mod Grabber

A simple, single-file **HTML + JavaScript tool** that helps Project Zomboid server admins grab **Workshop IDs** and **Mod IDs** from Steam URLs, IDs, or mod names. It auto-adds the leading `\` for **B42.13.1+** compatibility and generates ready-to-paste lines for `servertest.ini` / `server.ini`.

**Live Demo:** [https://yourusername.github.io/pz-mod-grabber/](https://yourusername.github.io/pz-mod-grabber/) (replace with your GitHub Pages link after enabling)

