## Features

- Add mods by **Workshop ID**, **full Steam URL**, or **mod name** (auto-searches Steam Workshop)
- Robust **Mod ID** extraction from description (with fallback to sanitized title)
- **Manual add** mode for cases where Steam API fetch fails (CORS issues)
- Auto-adds **leading `\`** to Mod IDs for **B42.13.1+** compatibility
- Responsive design (mobile-friendly)
- Copy-ready **WorkshopItems** and **Mods** lines

